Module RenderGrid
Header /Engine/Plugins/Experimental/RenderGrid/Source/RenderGrid/Public/RenderGrid/RenderGridQueue.h
Include #include "RenderGrid/RenderGridQueue.h"

Syntax

UCLASS (BlueprintType, Meta=(DontUseGenericSpawnObject="true"))  
class URenderGridQueue :  
    public UObject ,  
    public FTickableGameObject

Remarks

This class is responsible for rendering the given render grid jobs.

Variables

UE::RenderGrid::FRenderGridQueueCreateArgs Args The queue containing the render actions.
bool bCanceled Whether the queue has been canceled.
bool bFinished Whether the queue has been finished.
bool bPaused Whether the queue has been paused.
bool bStarted Whether the queue has been started yet.
TObjectPtr< URenderGridMoviePipelineRenderJob > CurrentEntry The movie pipeline render job that is currently being rendered.
TObjectPtr< URenderGridJob > CurrentJob The render grid jobs that is currently being rendered.
TMap< TObjectPtr< URenderGridJob >, TObjectPtr< URenderGridMoviePipelineRenderJob > > Entries The render grid jobs that are to be rendered, mapped to the movie pipeline render job of each specific render grid job.
FGuid Guid The unique ID of this queue.
FRenderGridPreviousEngineFpsSettings PreviousFrameLimitSettings The engine framerate settings values that have been overwritten by the currently applied engine framerate settings values.
FRenderGridManagerPreviousPropValues PreviousProps The property values that have been overwritten by the currently applied render grid job property values.
TSharedPtr< UE::RenderGrid::Private::FRenderGridGenericExecutionQueue > Queue The queue containing the render actions.
TArray< TObjectPtr< URenderGridJob > > RemainingJobs The render grid jobs that are to be rendered, removed when one is grabbed from it and added to the execution queue.
TObjectPtr< URenderGrid > RenderGrid The render grid of the given render grid job that will be rendered.
